                        <br>
                        <br>
                        　[[[ ROLL FOR YOUR FATE ]]]<br>
                        <br>
                        <br>
                        <br>
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class='row evi'><div class='col-sm-2 name'>evi@グラント</div><div class='col-sm-10 serif'>じゃあSHOTだ</div></div>
